THIRD-PARTY DATA AND ASSETS
================================================================================

This software uses third-party datasets and resources, each with their own
licensing terms as described below:

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Dataset: Game Recommendations on Steam
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Author:        Anton Kozyriev
Source:        https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/antonkozyriev/game-recommendations-on-steam
License:       CC0 1.0 Universal (CC0 1.0) Public Domain Dedication
DOI:           10.34740/KAGGLE/DS/2871694
Accessed:      January 2026
License Text:  https://creativecommons.org/publicdomain/zero/1.0/

Purpose:       Powers the collaborative filtering recommendation engine

Citation:      Kozyriev, A. (2023). Game Recommendations on Steam [Data set].
               Kaggle. https://doi.org/10.34740/KAGGLE/DS/2871694

Note:          This dataset is released under CC0 Public Domain, meaning it can
               be freely used, modified, and distributed without restrictions.
               Attribution is provided as a courtesy and best practice.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
External APIs
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This software integrates with the following third-party APIs, each subject to
their respective terms of service:

1. Steam APIs
   - Provider: Valve Corporation
   - Terms: https://steamcommunity.com/dev/apiterms
   - Purpose: User library synchronization (Steam Web API) and public game
              metadata (Steam Store API)

2. RAWG.io API
   - Provider: RAWG
   - Terms: https://rawg.io/apidocs
   - Purpose: Game metadata, covers, descriptions, and trending games

3. IsThereAnyDeal API
   - Provider: IsThereAnyDeal
   - Terms: https://docs.isthereanydeal.com
   - Purpose: Price tracking and deals information

4. SteamSpy API
   - Provider: SteamSpy
   - Terms: https://steamspy.com/api.php
   - Purpose: Public statistics on Steam games

5. GamerPower API
   - Provider: GamerPower
   - Terms: https://www.gamerpower.com/api-read
   - Purpose: Free game giveaways and promotions

6. Google Gemini API
   - Provider: Google
   - Terms: https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/terms
   - Purpose: AI-powered translation of game descriptions to Portuguese

Note: Use of these APIs requires compliance with their respective terms of
service. API keys must be obtained directly from providers.
